# Tauri dev-watcher ignores (gitignore syntax, relative to src-tauri/).
# Data the build scripts write under src-tauri/ is NOT source and must not
# trigger a cargo rebuild. The USDA food-DB build (scripts/build_fdc_db.py)
# downloads CSVs into scripts/.fdc_work/, which the `cargo tauri dev` watcher was
# picking up → repeated spurious rebuilds during iteration. Python scripts ship
# as bundled resources (copied at build time); editing them needs no rebuild.
scripts/.fdc_work/
scripts/*.csv
scripts/*.zip
